import React, { Suspense, useRef, useState, useEffect } from "react"
import { Canvas, useFrame } from "react-three-fiber"
import { ContactShadows, Environment, useGLTF, OrbitControls } from "drei"
import { HexColorPicker } from "react-colorful"
import { proxy, useProxy } from "valtio"
import Light from './component/Lights/index'
function Model(props) {
  const group = useRef()
  const { nodes, materials } = useGLTF('scene.gltf')
  return (
    <group ref={group} {...props} dispose={null}>
      <group rotation={[-Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh material={materials.hip} geometry={nodes.mesh_0.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.shoulder} geometry={nodes.mesh_1.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.calf_and_low} geometry={nodes.mesh_2.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.back_thigh} geometry={nodes.mesh_3.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.nose} geometry={nodes.mesh_4.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.back} geometry={nodes.mesh_5.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.head} geometry={nodes.mesh_6.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.front_thigh} geometry={nodes.mesh_7.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.neck} geometry={nodes.mesh_8.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.hand_tissue} geometry={nodes.mesh_9.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.chest_and_abs} geometry={nodes.mesh_10.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.front_lower_leg} geometry={nodes.mesh_11.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.inner_upper_thigh} geometry={nodes.mesh_12.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.feet_finger} geometry={nodes.mesh_13.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.lowerForearm} geometry={nodes.mesh_14.geometry} />
        <mesh material={materials.biceps} geometry={nodes.mesh_15.geometry} />
      </group>
    </group>
  )
}


export default function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Canvas  camera={{ position:[0,0,120], fov:65}}>
       
        <Suspense fallback={null}>
          <Model/>
        </Suspense>
      </Canvas>
    </>
  )
}
